                                   🗞️👨‍💼🗞️🧙 ALTERNATE CURRENT MOTORS 🧙🗞️👨‍💼🗞️

                                                       by⠀
                                              Electrical Engineer, The
                                        June 29th, 1888 Page number(s): 601

                                𝐀𝐋𝐓𝐄𝐑𝐍𝐀𝐓𝐄 𝐂𝐔𝐑𝐑𝐄𝐍𝐓 𝐌𝐎𝐓𝐎𝐑𝐒.—With reference to the
                                recent discoveries by Dr. Ferrari and Nikola Tesla in the
                                direction of alternate current motors, the question of prior
                                invention is cropping up already. We learn on good
                                authority that Prof. Elihu Thomson has had an alternate
                                current motor running in his laboratory for the last twelve
                                months or so.

