                                              [letter to the editor]
             

                          

                                 𝐈𝐭𝐬 𝐨𝐧𝐥𝐲 𝐑𝐢𝐯𝐚𝐥.—The only rival to the Tesla
                                 motor is the Keeley one; that would beat it, if it would
                                 work. The Keeley Company have called upon Mr. Keeley
                                 officially to disclose his secret, or henceforth and for ever
                                 hold his peace. He offered to do this eighteen months
                                 ago, and now is compelled to do so, or fall.  And he
                                 cannot do it.  The Keeley “motor” won’t “mote.”

