📰🧙📰 ON APPARATUS FOR CATHOGRAPHY 📰🧙📰
                  —————

             By NIKOLA TESLA
         Mining and Scientific Press
      May 9th, 1896 Page number(s): 378

______







‾‾‾‾‾‾
                   𝐍𝐎𝐓𝐄𝐒.
                    ———
[aka ANNOUNCEMENT REGARDING VACUUM TUBE LIGHTING]

  📰👨‍💼📰🧙                        🧙📰👨‍💼📰 

                     by⠀
