‾‾‾

🎞️ Sometime on July 19th 1896:

Tesla tours the recently installed Westinghouse Niagara Falls hydroelectric plant based on 9 of his patents.

He signs the visitor log: '''Nikola Tesla, Stop in New York but heart is at Niagara.'''

