       # MAGNETIC MOTOR
         TAPS 'THIRD FORCE' #
            —————
 Prof. Ehrenhaft Demonstrates
    First Operation by Current
    From Permanent Magnet
            —————

“ROCHESTER, June 24 -- What was said to be the first magnetic motor, operating purely on magnetic current supplied by a permanent magnet, was demonstrated here today before the meeting of the American Physical Society at the University of Rochester by Prof. Felix Ehrenhaft, who recently startled the scientific world with experiments which, he maintains, provide proof for the existence of pure magnetic current.”…
______



   New York Times, The   July 30th, 1944

           SCIENCE IN REVIEW
                —————
# A Physicist Supports His Hypothesis That
Magnetic Currents Flow Through Universe #
                —————
“Physicists attending the recent meeting of the American Physical Society at the University of Rochester (N. Y.) watched Prof. Felix Ehrenhaft present the most dramatic evidence so far in support of his hypothesis that "not only electric currents but also magnetic currents flow through the universe.”…
______



